   <title>
    屯門公路兩警員駕電單車撞貨Van 司機入稟索償
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%85%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%A7%95%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E8%B2%A8van-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F
   </link>
   <description>
    <![CDATA[<div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-18 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">內容: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/5030">政經</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F22_28.jpg" width="940" height="492" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-19 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">自由標籤: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/529141">警察</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/526031">交通意外</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/court">法庭</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/528473">獨媒報導</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><font color="#e4692b">【獨媒報導】</font>大前年4月，於屯門公路出九龍近深井對開路段，兩名警員駕駛電單車撞向前方一輛輕型貨車，導致後車窗爆裂。該輕型貨車司機上周五（19日）入稟區域法院，向涉事兩名警員索償。</p>
<p>原告人為 Lee Kam Lun Lawrence，被告人有3名，分別為：警務處處長、兩名涉事警員 Fong Kam Wa 及 Wong Kam Hung。</p>
<p>據入稟狀指，原告人就兩名被告人於2021年4月23日在屯門公路疏忽駕駛，而導致的交通意外之損害索償，至於警務處處長則有替代責任。</p>
<p>案件編號：DCPI 1213/2024</p>
